original_title: Sashihara Rino Graduation Concert 〜Sayonara Sashihara Rino〜
overview: Sashihara Rino Graduation Concert 〜Sayonara Sashihara Rino〜 (〜指原莉乃 卒業コンサート ~さよなら、指原莉乃〜) is Sashihara Rino's graduation concert. This concert was held at Yokohama Stadium on April 28, 2019.
title: Sashihara Rino Graduation Concert 〜Sayonara Sashihara Rino〜
